title: match not starting
body: I was in the character selection window before a ranked match. after everyone had chose their champion and the timer went off. the match didnt start and when i relog it just has the button recconect and when i click it, it does nothing. can confirm not me coz i am duo q and friend also same plz help rito

replies.body: Same thing here, just started a game but we were stuck in champ select for about 5minutes after picks. Loading in now though though. Someone said that left last game because of the same thing and got given a loss.
